{
  "stem": "13693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if I would tell them too much, I was scared that I would be exposed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this can go a little further, and I could lose my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I-- I told my friends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and to live in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, now now we're starting a different type of philosophy [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ghetto is transforming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It remains only 15,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The ghetto became-- became [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] matured.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The philosophy to go as sheep to slaughter, changes in the philosophy of partial resistance.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used what was really [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] politically oriented.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's starting to-- I'm sorry-- organize, and to produce [? some cells. ?] And we're gradually--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Cells.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Resistance cells.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by thinking about doing some-- some even-- even to send up against the German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we have-- we are starting to think about getting out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the outside world is numb and dumb.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It does not listen to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There's a lot of hate from-- from-- from the surrounding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By going in here, first of all, by organizing-- we are probably, Vlina was the first organized resistance.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vlina was sending out [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This means-- some--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--emissaries to Warsaw, to to gather stock.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is the resistance in here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vlina at that time, has such great people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Gleuck ?] is producing his partisan, and--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Abakovna. ?] You have Wittenberg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have you have-- the young [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I was part of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "OK--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the thing is, gradually-- gradually, it was developed in here the idea of [NON-ENGLISH]-- we don't have a choice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you're-- and maturing.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
